<div class="container-fluid" id="network">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-3" id="sidebar">
			<input type="text" id="search" class="form-control" placeholder="輸入系所名稱">
			<button id="search_submit" class="btn btn-default">Search</button>
			<p>Link threshold</p>
			
			<div class="range-slider">
				<input id="threshold" type="range" id="thersholdSlider" name="points" class="range-slider__range" value="5" min="5" max="20">
				<span class="range-slider__value">5</span>
			</div>
			<form id="group">
				<p>colored by:</p>
				<!-- <input type="radio" name="group" id="cluster" value="cluster" class="form-control">
				<label for="cluster">Cluster</label> -->
				<input type="radio" name="group" id="field" value="field" class="form-control" checked>
				<label for="field">Field</label>
				<input type="radio" name="group" id="level" value="level" class="form-control">
				<label for="level">Level</label>
			</form>
			<h4 class="node-name"><a href="#">　</a></h4>
			<div id="legend">
			</div>

			<span class="info">
				<a href="#" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#infoModal">
					<i class="fa fa-question-circle fa-lg" aria-hidden="true"></i>
				</a>
			</span>
			<div id="infoModal" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
			  <div class="modal-dialog">

			    <!-- Modal content-->
			    <div class="modal-content">
			      <div class="modal-header">
			        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
			        <h4 class="modal-title">使用說明</h4>
			      </div>
			      <div class="modal-body">
			        <h4>這是什麼？</h4>
					<ul>
						<li>圖中每個點代表一個一間系所，連結代表共同被選取的次數，越粗則次數越多</li>
					</ul>

					<h4>操作說明：</h4>
					<ul>
						<li>搜尋系所會將畫面中心移至該系所，並將點放大</li>
						<li>調整連結的threshold，過濾掉較弱的連結</li>
						<li>調整分群，以不同的指標為系所上色</li>
					</ul>
			      </div>
			      <div class="modal-footer">
			        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
			      </div>
			    </div>

			  </div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-9">
			<div id="force">
				<h4 id="spinner_text">若載入過久，請重新整理</h4>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
